HEADWORD: mucosa
<hw>mucosa</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The mucus-secreting membrane lining
all body cavities or passages that communicate with the exterior; called
also <altname>mucous membrane</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mucous membrane.</syn>⟦br⟧
